---
description: WEEX repository routing and safety rules
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use `skills/weex-trader-skill` for WEEX execution, profile, vault, and live REST workflows.
- Use `skills/weex-analysis-skill` for read-only analysis of normalized snapshots and fills.
- Never send mutating WEEX requests without explicit user confirmation.
- Prefer secret transport that avoids putting credentials or vault passwords directly on argv.
